Tips for using Resurrection

- check out the files in include/Resurrection/conf.h - they allow you to set a
  few options for the applications.

Rwm
---
- click on the title bar of a window to give the client input focus.
- ctrl + left click on titlebar - shade/unshade
- shift + left click on titlebar - kill window
- ctrl + left click on titlebar - close window
- left click on titlebar - raise
- right click on titlebar - lower
